window.bookSummaryJSON = "Francine Rivers is one of America's favorite romance writers and a best-selling inspirational author. Her many heartfelt novels have won awards and the adoration of fans accross the country. In <i>Redeeming Love</i>, she retells the Biblical story of Hosea, setting it in the 1850s, amidst California's gold country."; 
